text: LA-3 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by the Choudhary Muhammad Saeed of Pakistan Muslim League (N). It covers the area of Mirpur city in Mirpur District of Azad Kashmir, Pakistan. Category:Mirpur District ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016. Category:Government of Azad Kashmir Category:Constituencies of Pakistan
title: Constituency LA-3
